dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Clark. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Tiffany Ross.
Nice to meet you, Tiffany. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim regarding a recent incident.
Of course, Tiffany. Can you please provide me with your policy number and the date of the incident in dd/mm/yyyy format?
Sure, my policy number is five six two three four one and the incident happened on twelve zero four two zero two two.
Thank you, Tiffany. I will start the claim process with the information you provided. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Tiffany. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
